 Mental health advocate Nic Newling struggled through the confusing highs and depressing lows of an undiagnosed bipolar disorder between the ages of 13 and 18 .
It was the unexpected and tragic death of his teenage brother , Christopher , who killed himself amidst his battle with mental illnesses .
Now the 28-year-old is using his story of loss and confusion he moved between doctors and psychiatric wards to raise awareness of mental illness .